        "sender_full_name": "Rishi Gupta",
        "timestamp": 1522444897
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Right now the headers have <code>margin: 10px 0</code>, and will be changed to <code>margin:10px 0 0 0</code>, so it doesn't push the related content away. Is this what you mean by fixing the vertical spacing?</p>",
        "id": 552663,
        "sender_full_name": "Gooca",
        "timestamp": 1522445114
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>there's currently too much space between the headers and the first element in their section. Possibly that'll fix it?</p>",
