        "content": "<p>Bootstrap's <code>margin: 10px 0;</code> interacts with the <code>input-group: margin:20px 0;</code>so the elements end up 30px away. Changing to this <code>input-group: margin: 0 0 10px 0; </code> gives 10 pixels between the first element and the heading. <a href=\"/user_uploads/2/fa/r3MGOzfYAq8ekElWupVZoDE9/Screenshot-from-2018-03-30-17-59-35.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screenshot-from-2018-03-30-17-59-35.png\">Screenshot-from-2018-03-30-17-59-35.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/fa/r3MGOzfYAq8ekElWupVZoDE9/Screenshot-from-2018-03-30-17-59-35.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screenshot-from-2018-03-30-17-59-35.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/fa/r3MGOzfYAq8ekElWupVZoDE9/Screenshot-from-2018-03-30-17-59-35.png\"></a></div>",
